01:03:04,503 --> 01:03:06,272
And me,

786
01:03:07,043 --> 01:03:09,142
Jin Do Jun.

787
01:03:10,583 --> 01:03:13,443
They're my mother and father,.

788
01:03:24,793 --> 01:03:27,932
   

789
01:03:28,538 --> 01:03:31,341
I should get a wedding gift for my eldest grandson.

790
01:03:31,341 --> 01:03:32,876
Is there anything you need?

791
01:03:32,876 --> 01:03:36,442
We'll start out at Jeongsimjae, so we don't need anything.

792
01:03:36,442 --> 01:03:38,343
No, don't say that.

793
01:03:38,343 --> 01:03:41,343
You are becoming a real adult, Seong Jun.

794
01:03:41,343 --> 01:03:44,512
I must do something for you.

795
01:03:44,512 --> 01:03:46,942
Tell me what you want.

796
01:03:46,942 --> 01:03:49,183
Then Grandfather,

797
01:03:49,183 --> 01:03:55,783
please give me the right to play a part as one of the adults in the family.

798
01:03:56,599 --> 01:03:59,193
As one of the adults in the family? It's no big deal.

799
01:03:59,193 --> 01:04:01,762
It's about taking responsibility.

800
01:04:01,762 --> 01:04:05,432
If Seong Jun wishes to share the burden with us,

801
01:04:05,432 --> 01:04:08,633
he should get some shares too. Right, Dong Ki?

802
01:04:08,633 --> 01:04:12,202
Yes, sure thing.

803
01:04:12,202 --> 01:04:15,673
So? Did Father say he'd give him some?

804
01:04:15,673 --> 01:04:17,282
Of course.

805
01:04:17,282 --> 01:04:23,513
I think he wants to announce it at the reception when the whole family is there.

806
01:04:24,352 --> 01:04:25,528
Hwa Young.

807
01:04:25,528 --> 01:04:30,363
Have a drink with me at the reception. It's been too long.

808
01:04:30,363 --> 01:04:34,033
Sounds like it'll be a coronation ceremony, not a wedding.

809
01:04:34,963 --> 01:04:37,163
Will Father really announce

810
01:04:37,163 --> 01:04:41,414
at the wedding that Seong Jun is next in line for the throne?

811
01:04:44,302 --> 01:04:47,613
Of course, Seong Jun is his eldest grandson.

812
01:04:47,613 --> 01:04:51,042
Your father will take great care of him.

813
01:04:51,042 --> 01:04:54,113
All right. Don't be late.

814
01:04:54,113 --> 01:04:56,883
I'll see you at the wedding.

815
01:04:59,095 --> 01:05:01,093
About Seong Jun's fiancee.

816
01:05:01,093 --> 01:05:03,122
I should ask her to visit us tomorrow.

817
01:05:03,122 --> 01:05:07,533
Why? Do you already want to be an overbearing mother-in-law?

818
01:05:08,233 --> 01:05:11,803
No, I want to be a good daughter-in-law to you.

819
01:05:11,803 --> 01:05:16,733
All your paintings are too good to be just kept in this room.

820
01:05:16,733 --> 01:05:18,403
You should have a solo show.

821
01:05:18,403 --> 01:05:20,173
Your granddaughter-in-law runs a gallery.

822
01:05:20,173 --> 01:05:23,486
Gosh, stop. A solo show? Please.

823
01:05:23,486 --> 01:05:25,655
This is just an old lady's hobby.

824
01:05:25,655 --> 01:05:29,159
Don't be so modest. You should think about it, Mother.

825
01:05:29,159 --> 01:05:32,362
Jeong Rae, has Mr. Yang called?

826
01:05:32,362 --> 01:05:35,899
He said he'd be home by lunch. How come he's not back yet?

827
01:05:35,899 --> 01:05:37,363
Oh, you're right.

828
01:05:37,363 --> 01:05:40,523
Father always calls if he's going to be home late.

829
01:05:55,772 --> 01:05:56,943
I received a call from Jeongsimjae.

830
01:05:56,943 --> 01:06:00,083
They're asking when the chairman will be home.

831
01:06:00,083 --> 01:06:02,782
What should I tell them, Sir?

832
01:06:13,670 --> 01:06:19,132
 We found a brain arteriovenous malformation, Sir. 

833
01:06:20,403 --> 01:06:23,172
 Will surgery fix it? 

834
01:06:23,172 --> 01:06:25,873
 The thing is... 

835
01:06:25,873 --> 01:06:31,013
 The location is quite risky if we were to perform surgery. 

836
01:06:31,013 --> 01:06:38,513
 So I have no choice but to rely on luck. 

837
01:06:41,693 --> 01:06:43,622
 Is that it? 

838
01:06:44,463 --> 01:06:48,593
 We will do our very best to monitor it closely. 

839
01:06:50,003 --> 01:06:52,833
In my head,

840
01:06:54,173 --> 01:07:00,603
there is a ticking time bomb waiting to go off.

