♫   Please remember, the other side of me   ♫

844
01:08:10,840 --> 01:08:14,070
♫   I won't let go of   ♫

845
01:08:14,070 --> 01:08:19,610
♫   A love we both wanted just like this   ♫

846
01:08:19,610 --> 01:08:23,560
♫   We loved each other   ♫

847
01:08:23,560 --> 01:08:28,863
 As you ordered, I prepared a share transfer agreement for Mr. Jin Seong Jun. 

848
01:08:28,863 --> 01:08:30,302
 Chairman! 

849
01:08:30,302 --> 01:08:31,541
   

850
01:08:31,541 --> 01:08:36,211
 Don't you know whom I love the most out of all my children? 

851
01:08:36,211 --> 01:08:38,243
 What on earth did you do? 

852
01:08:38,243 --> 01:08:43,436
 The one who can make Soonyang bigger and better than I can will get everything. 

853
01:08:43,436 --> 01:08:46,282
 That Do Jun takes after me. 

854
01:08:46,282 --> 01:08:49,383
 Do you think that makes sense? 

855
01:08:49,383 --> 01:08:51,783
 Grandfather, you were right. 

856
01:08:51,783 --> 01:08:54,697
 I've given up on my goal of buying Soonyang with my money. 

857
01:08:54,697 --> 01:08:56,222
 Do not step over the line! 

858
01:08:56,222 --> 01:09:01,133
 You guys are different from us. 

859
01:09:01,938 --> 01:09:06,940
 Don't you dare delude yourself into thinking that you can be a rightful heir. 

